cs.SY, cs.LG, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.DC 

This paper deals with networked control systems and proposes a deep reinforcement learning-based algorithm for scheduling. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SY (Systems and Control), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), as the algorithm is based on deep reinforcement learning. The paper also mentions cyber-physical systems and Internet of Things, which suggests that it could belong to cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). Additionally, the paper uses optimal controllers and resource allocation, which are related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
